@node 006_1

v1.6
        New: PlayerControl
        Bew: DeliTracker Support
        Fix: Save now works correct
        New: New LVData format (mode added)
        New: Now supports the new PlayGUI MPeg/midi functions
        New: Skin.txt support
        New: internal (sample/midi) and mp3 suffix filecheck for 'add files'
        New: mp3 TAG support (whitout Genre)
        New: Play16 support + Prefs
        New: MPegA Support + Prefs
        Fix: Add Directory Function fixed
        New: Now, default lv_pic and op_pic avaible. You can load
             a skin whitout this images! (only back image used)
        New: Start Hip/DeliTracker when needed
        New: Simple ASCII Export
        New: Converter
        New: Comments for Samples avaible
        New: Add Line
        New: GMPlay (MIDI) Support + Prefs
        New: Fixed Version String



@endnode

@node 006_2

v1.5

        - PLoneEd is now a part of PLone
        - Play mods whit Hippoplayer if PlayGui not found
        - Helpsystem
        - Requester ask you before clear all Data
        - Backgroundpattern for some Windows
        - PLone Listfiles now checked before loaded
        - New Function 'Add Directory'
        - Some changes
        - Hide/Show Gadgets function
          (from PlayGUI :*)
        - Settings Window


v1.4

 - When PLone quits, a Requester will open and you can save the List
 - Sourcecode changed
 - Import Lists opens a Requester for Composer's name
 - Press Play to play the mod direct.
 - no sounderrors when play a mod and then select a sample.


1.3:

 - List can be save/loaded now also among other things names.
 - Save new contain function now also in the menu
 - The PLone window is now a AppWindow. (drag and drop)
 - The ListView is activated now on start.
   No more message that the Listview of the false type is.
 - Export now as Eagleplayer PYSION
 - New ToolTypes Defcomment/Defcomposer sets default text for
   composer/comment with ADD files function
 - Menue's have now all Shortcut's
 - Numeric key block keys (partly) are supported
 - New Amigaguide documentation (German/English)
 - Some small modifications made
 - New lists can be created
 - Import of Hippoplayer/DeliTracker Playlists
 - after changing a Entry, the List will not be jump to the beginning first.


1.2b:

 - 2 errors recovered (ToolTypes were not stored (rexxc:rx required)
   and PLoneEd was sometimes not found.)
 - A false skin drawer indicated gets the user a message.

1.2:

 - Samples can now also in would list with to be taken up.
   (with the restriction no comment to be input can)
 - PLone produces now an ASSIGN PLone:  (for PlayGui)
 - The error, that after termination and restart of PLone the old
   entries again in the Edit window were were recovered
   (thanks to Richard Kapp)
 - The list can be saveed now as HippoPlayer or Delitracker PlayList.
 - With ADD FILE aborted was inserted an empty entry.
 - Default path for Filerequester can be now indicated.
   (again thanks to Richard Kapp)
 - The preset Skin not found opens a Filerequester for the selection of
   another Skins.

   And now finally with the Template Pics to create own Skins!!

1.1:

 - There were unfortunately some problems if PlayGui before PLone was started:
   - Launcher was found, could not not store the ToolTypes
   - Skin's could not be loaded
 - Comment the field in the PLoneEd window does not show now no more the
   path of the Modules on (Grummel).
 - PLoneEd is terminated now also terminated if PLone
 - An entry modified no more to the at the beginning of the list one branches
   now, but one remains with the modified entry


1.0:

- first release

@endnode

