@node 007_2
About PlayGui

     PlayGUI is a kind of GUI-replacement for Play16 and HIPPO-Player
     - but it has some very unique features, like Skinsupport...;)

     Developed by Richard Kapp
     and avaible on Aminet or on the @{"Website" link 005_1}.

