@node 000_1
The Converter

Use this little Tool to convert the old PLone PlayLists (1.0-1.5) to the new
1.6 format.

First requester: Select the old PlayList
Second Requester: Select the new filename

To Quit, press the Filerequester  cancel Button 

@endnode

@node 4_6
The Skins

a default Skin have 3 Pictures in a directory:

---

back     - The Mainpic
lv_pic   - The Listview move buttons
op_pic   - The functionbuttons 

---

There are 2 more Pictures optional inside the Skindrawer:

---

background   - Background pattern for some windows (about, settings)
playerctrl   - The Picture for the PlayerControl Window

---

Since v1.6 of PLone, a Skin can have only the back picture. The lv_pic and 
op_pic will be loaded from the def/ drawer

@endnode


